WEBVTT

00:12:57.320 --> 00:13:01.800
that he would never pin
a boutonniere on his son's tuxedo lapel.

00:13:03.480 --> 00:13:05.616
The weeks before the dance,

00:13:05.640 --> 00:13:06.896
the house is in a flurry,

00:13:06.920 --> 00:13:09.696
and I don't know who's more excited,
the staff or the kids.

00:13:09.720 --> 00:13:10.856
(Laughter)

00:13:10.880 --> 00:13:12.496
The night of the event

00:13:12.520 --> 00:13:16.976
involves rides in vintage cars,

00:13:17.000 --> 00:13:18.976
a walk on a red carpet

00:13:19.000 --> 00:13:21.496
into the great room,

00:13:21.520 --> 00:13:23.320
a terrific DJ

00:13:24.160 --> 00:13:25.936
and a photographer at the ready

00:13:25.960 --> 00:13:28.496
to capture pictures of these attendees

00:13:28.520 --> 00:13:29.880
and their families.